name: WELL Health Technologies Corp. 5.50% Convertible Senior Unsecured Debentures
longDescription: WELL Health Technologies Corp is the owner and operator of a portfolio of Primary Hclinics delivering healthcare-related services It operates through below segments: clinical operations and allied health, Electronic medical record (EMR), Billing and revenue cycle management solutions, Digital apps, Cybersecurity, CRH, MyHealth, and corporate/shared services. Its segments are grouped in three divisions; Omni-channel Patient Services - Primary includes clinical operations and allied health. Omni-channel Patient Services - Specialized comprises CRH and MyHealth under two segments. Virtual Services include EMR, billing and revenue cycle management solutions, digital apps, and cybersecurity.
